'''PlayStation 3 系统软件'''是指[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]可升级系统软件以及PS3的[[操作系统|操作系统]]。

PlayStation 3本机操作系统被称作“Cell OS”，据信是建基于 [[FreeBSD|FreeBSD]]计划<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.netresec.com/?page=Blog&month=2011-01&post=DFRWS-2009-Network-Forensics |title="DFRWS 2009 Network Forensics", NETRESEC Network Security Blog, 2011 |accessdate=2011-12-18 |archive-date=2012-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120317115055/http://www.netresec.com/?page=Blog&month=2011-01&post=DFRWS-2009-Network-Forensics |dead-url=no }}</ref>。用于PlayStation 3的[[List_of_3D_graphics_APIs|三维计算机图形API]]软件“LibGCM”和[[PSGL|PSGL]]，则是基于[[OpenGL_ES|OpenGL ES]]以及[[Nvidia|Nvidia]]旗下开发的[[Cg語言|Cg语言]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.khronos.org/developers/library/siggraph2006/OpenGL_ES_BOF/OpenGL-ES-Demos.ppt |title=SONY/Khronos OpenGL ES/PSGL Presentation in PPT format |accessdate=2011-12-18 |archive-date=2012-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131143448/http://www.khronos.org/developers/library/siggraph2006/OpenGL_ES_BOF/OpenGL-ES-Demos.ppt |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
PlayStation 3以“[[XMB|XrossMediaBar]]”（交叉媒体廊）作为其[[图形用户界面|图形用户界面]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=PS3™ {{!}} XMB™（交叉媒體廊）之基本操作|url=http://ps3.tgbus.com/zt/manual/basicoperations/xmb.html|publisher=电玩巴士|accessdate=2013-11-25|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202234750/http://ps3.tgbus.com/zt/manual/basicoperations/xmb.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

